  "body": "# ðŸš€ Feature Request\r\n\r\n### Description\r\n### Describe the solution you'd like\r\n\r\nLogging a countdown till the next validator scheduled operation across all validator public keys the process is assigned. A prometheus metric might not be a bad idea too.\r\n\r\nI think it'll make for better ability to time upgrade and minor restarts, without losing on valuable profits, in particular proposing a block.\r\n\r\n### Describe alternatives you've considered\r\n\r\nAt the moment there are no alternative, and a simple upgrade restart, or a config change, can cost you your spot at proposing a block and enjoy the greater financial incentives it brings with it.\r\n",
